A '''fruit plantation''' is a primary industry that only appears in the [[en/Manual/Climates]]. It produces [[en/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Fruit]] which should be delivered to a [[en/Manual/Base Set/Industries/Food Processing Plant]], but does not accept any cargo. Fruit plantations can only be built in grassy non-desert areas.

